OL,3,CPrimary school forced to shut after
OL,4,Chuge fire breaks out at the site
OL,6,FA primary school has been forced to
OL,7,Fshut after a major fire broke out at
OL,8,Fthe site on Wednesday morning. Fire
OL,9,Fcrews attended the blaze at St Athan
OL,10,FPrimary School in the Vale of
OL,11,FGlamorgan, where hundreds of people
OL,12,Fwere evacuated from the scene.
OL,14,FVideo footage supplied by South Wales
OL,15,FFire and Rescue Service shows the
OL,16,Fschool has been completely gutted.
OL,18,FThe service says the blaze is now
OL,19,Fcontained within an ICT suite at the
OL,20,Fschool.
