OL,6,FVale of Glamorgan Chief Executive Rob
OL,7,FThomas confirmed the school would be
OL,8,Fclosed for the rest of the week, with
OL,9,Ffire crews still at the scene of the
OL,10,Fincident.
OL,12,FCllr Thomas said the fast reactions of
OL,13,Femergency responders helped ensure "a
OL,14,Fserious situation did not become
OL,15,Ftragic", with nobody hurt as a result
OL,16,Fof the incident.
