OL,6,FFive fire appliances, and other
OL,7,Fspecialist units, were sent to deal
OL,8,Fwith the blaze. The school will now
OL,9,Fwork with the local authority and the
OL,10,Ffire service to assess the damage.
OL,12,FThe council confirmed on Wednesday
OL,13,Farrangements would be made with
OL,14,Fparents and carers regarding teaching
OL,15,Ffor the rest of the week.
OL,17,FCllr Thomas said: "After news of a
OL,18,Ffire at St Athan Primary School broke
OL,19,Fearlier today the only thing that
OL,20,Fmattered was that no one was hurt.
