OL,6,F"Thankfully, the professionalism of
OL,7,Fstaff, who quickly followed emergency
OL,8,Fprotocols, along with the swift
OL,9,Fattendance of South Wales Fire and
OL,10,FRescue Service, ensured this was the
OL,11,Fcase.
OL,13,F"I'd like to recognise those
OL,14,Findividuals for that response, which
OL,15,Fmeant a serious situation did not
OL,16,Fbecome tragic. Thank you for your
OL,17,Factions, I know I speak for the entire
OL,18,Fcommunity when I say we are extremely
OL,19,Fgrateful."
