OL,6,FA spokesperson for South Wales Fire
OL,7,Fand Rescue Service said: "Today at
OL,8,Fapproximately 11.48am, South Wales
OL,9,FFire and Rescue Service responded to a
OL,10,Freport of a fire at St Athan Primary
OL,11,FSchool.
OL,13,F"SWFRS mobilised five fire engines,
OL,14,Ftwo water bowsers, and several
OL,15,Fspecialist officers to bring the fire
OL,16,Funder control. The fire is now
OL,17,Fcontained to a small block of
OL,18,Fclassrooms and an ICT suite.
