OL,3,CPrimary school forced to shut after
OL,4,Chuge fire breaks out at the site
OL,6,F"Crews are exposing the roof area
OL,7,Fwhere the fire originated to prevent
OL,8,Ffurther fire spread, heat and smoke
OL,9,Fdamage. Approximately 240 pupils,
OL,10,Fteaching staff and contractors were
OL,11,Fsafely evacuated from the school, and
OL,12,Fthere are no reports of any injuries.
OL,14,F"We are working with on-site
OL,15,Fcontractors and local authority
OL,16,Feducation staff to establish the cause
OL,17,Fof the fire. Local authority personnel
OL,18,Fare invoking their education
OL,19,Fcontinuity plans and will release
OL,20,Finformation on these in due course."
